headline: S&P Global Introduces CreditCompanion™, Enhancing RatingsDirect® on S&P Capital IQ Pro with Advanced AI Technology
summary: S&P Global today announced the launch of CreditCompanion™, a Generative Artificial Intelligence (GenAI) powered application for its RatingsDirect® on S&P Capital IQ Pro platform. This first release of CreditCompanion™ simplifies the process of researching the credit risk of entities, securities and credit markets S&P Global Ratings provides through RatingsDirect®, the flagship platform of S&P Global Ratings' credit ratings and research, with future enhancements planned.
